VOTABLE.DESCRIPTION: Mukulski Archive for Space Telescopes (MAST) archive.stsci.edu send questions to: archive@stsci.edu

PARAM.name: voclass
PARAM.DESCRIPTION: VO Data model name and version

FIELD.name: tstart
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Time of start of exposure in MJD

FIELD.name: title
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: data set name and target name

FIELD.name: ds_ident
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: data set identifier (using format approved by ADEC)

FIELD.name: spec_fil
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: actual coverage divided by total bandpass

FIELD.name: spec_rp
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Resolving Power (i.e., W divided by dW)

FIELD.name: s_fov
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Approximate size of region in degrees (based on largest dimension of aperture)

FIELD.name: aperture
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: aperture dimensions (length x width) or just diameter

FIELD.name: spectralsi
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: SI scale factor and dimensions for spectral coordinate (i.e. wavelengths)

FIELD.name: fluxsi
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: SI scale factor and dimensions for fluxes

FIELD.name: fluxcal
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Defines type of calibration used for flux values
